label: Schistosoma mansoni eggs per gram, by microscopy
definition: Eggs per gram (epg) of S. mansoni eggs from Kato-Katz (KK) test, first slide. Each participant contributed a maximum of three stool samples and Schistosoma are assessed from up to three slides per sample (by microscopy, by microscopy 2nd, by microscopy 3rd).
